title: Mike Nayna | Bret Weinstein's DarkHorse Podcast #7
description:
Award winning documentary filmmaker, Mike Nayna sits down with Bret Weinstein on the DarkHorse Podcast to discuss his documentary on the infamous situation at The Evergreen State College, as well as his current work documenting the scandal surrounding the Grievance Studies. 

Please subscribe to the channel and hit the notification bell.
